There is still much work to be done in Gorgoroth! The Allegiances of the Free-peoples seek adventurers to continue the work of gaining control of the region. Report to your Allegiance's Expedition Organizer to find out how you can help.
Expedition Organizers can be found in Allegiance Halls. They are Vórthi, Glórellas, Tancram, and Aster Hayward.\n\nYou should talk to your Expedition Organizer.
Travel to the Ruins of Díngarth

'Greetings. There is still much work ahead of us, and I have been assigned to determine areas most in need of your assistance. Report to me each day for a new expedition assignment. You can then visit the Bounty Boards for specific tasks, though the boards here will only have tasks for that day's Expedition. If you wish to do more, you can find Bounty Boards in each region of Gorgoroth with additional threats.'
